(Per year at full utilization) Tj
T*
(- Tail issuance: 0.25 * 262,800 = 65,700 ATHO/year) Tj
T*
(- Total annual fees at floor: 147,825 ATHO/year) Tj
T*
(- Annual burn-path max \(80%\): 118,260 ATHO/year) Tj
T*
(- Annual net formula: Delta_year = 65,700 - \(118,260 * utilization\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Deflation Threshold) Tj
T*
(Set annual net to zero:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(65,700 - 118,260u = 0) Tj
T*
(u = 65,700 / 118,260 ~= 0.5556) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(So:) Tj
T*
(- <55.56%: inflationary protocol net.) Tj
T*
(- =55.56%: neutral.) Tj
T*
(- >55.56%: deflationary protocol net \(until floor clipping binds\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
